title: S15 Ep73: Salem's Supernatural Secrets with Lara & Daniel Fury
itunes:title: Salem's Supernatural Secrets with Lara & Daniel Fury
description:
Darkness Radio shares Salem's Supernatural Secrets with Lara & Daniel Fury

You THINK you know the stories of Salem, MA...well, you only know part of the story, fragments of the history, hauntings and high strangeness. Today we touch on the Salem Witch stories but go deeper than we ever have, our guests also reveal remarkable stories of curses, hauntings, murder and mayhem in America's Witchcraft capital.

Visit their site and take their tours here:
www.blackcatsalem.com

Order their book here: https://amazon.com
